main event: Two blue-green lights were sighted traveling parallel in Phoenix, Arizona on July 16, 1952.
interesting points: The lights were observed for approximately 10 seconds at about 2107H,The pilot estimated the objects were traveling at an undetermined speed greater than a fighter plane,The objects traveled from an altitude of approximately 7700 to 5500 feet over a distance of 10 miles,The weather conditions were clear with good visibility at the time of the sighting,The objects were not identified as ordinary aircraft according to the observing pilot's experience.
witness description: a pilot from the 127th Pilot Training Wing
